==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Modifier
<hw>Mod"i*fi`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who, or that which, modifies.</def> <rj><au>Hume.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Gram.)</fld> <def>A word or phrase that modifies
another word, phrase, or sentence, usually by limiting the scope or
restricting the meaning of the sentence element modified.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Modify</ent>⟦br⟧
